<h1>Steps of Meditation</h1>
<img src="https://www.sahajayogaportal.org/images/portal/realization/aydinlanma-meditasyonu-1.jpg" />
<p>Put your right hand on your heart<br />
    Ask 3 times the motherly energy<br />
    Kundalini within you:<br />
    "Mother, am I the spirit?" </p>
<img src="https://www.sahajayogaportal.org/images/portal/realization/aydinlanma-meditasyonu-2.jpg" />
<p>Put your right hand under the ribs<br />
    on the feft-hand side. Ask inside 3 times:<br />
    "Mother, am I my own mster?"
    </p>
<img src="https://www.sahajayogaportal.org/images/portal/realization/aydinlanma-meditasyonu-3.jpg" />
<p>Put your right hand on the left groin<br />
    and ask inside 6 times:<br />
    "Mother, please give me<br />
    the pure knowledge"</p>
<img src="https://www.sahajayogaportal.org/images/portal/realization/aydinlanma-meditasyonu-4.jpg" />
<p>Put your right hand under the ribs<br />
    on the feft-hand side. Say 10 times:<br />
    "Mother, I am my own master"</p> 
<img src="https://www.sahajayogaportal.org/images/portal/realization/aydinlanma-meditasyonu-5.jpg" />
<p>Put your right hand on your heart<br />
    and repeat inside 12 times<br />
    "Mother, I am the pure spirit"</p>  
<img src="https://www.sahajayogaportal.org/images/portal/realization/aydinlanma-meditasyonu-6.jpg" />
<p>Put your right hand on the corner<br />
    of your neck and the left shoulder,<br />
    turn your head to the right.<br />
    Say inside 16 times:<br />
    "Mother, I am not guilty at all".</p>  
<img src="https://www.sahajayogaportal.org/images/portal/realization/aydinlanma-meditasyonu-7.jpg" />
<p>Put your right hand on your forehead,<br />
    bend down your head<br />
    and say a few times:<br />
    "Mother, I forgive everyone<br />
    including myself"</p>  
<img src="https://www.sahajayogaportal.org/images/portal/realization/aydinlanma-meditasyonu-8.jpg" />
<p>Put your right hand on the back of your head,<br />
    push your head back and say,<br />
    "Oh, Divine Power, if I have comitted<br />
    any mistakes, please forgive me"</p>  
<img src="https://www.sahajayogaportal.org/images/portal/realization/aydinlanma-meditasyonu-9.jpg" />
<p>Open your hand fully and press<br />
    on the fontanelle bone area.<br />
    Move it slowly clockwise 7 times,<br />
    so that you move your scalp together with the hand.<br />
    Each time repeat:<br />
    "Mother, please give me my Self-Realization" </p>       